### ── ADMIN SERVICE (/admin) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### All operations require the Admin role.

### 1. List users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Users
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 2. List roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Roles
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. List branches
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Branches
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 4. Create new branch
# @name createBranch
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/createBranch
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "STU",
  "name": "AutoMarkt Stuttgart",
  "address": "Koenigstrasse 5",
  "city": "Stuttgart",
  "country": "Germany",
  "region": "Baden-Wuerttemberg"
}

### 5. Update branch
### branchId: replace with ID returned from step 4
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/updateBranch
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branchId": "fa2f6315-6576-404b-ae58-47c9e1769657",
  "name": "AutoMarkt Stuttgart Zentrum",
  "address": "Koenigstrasse 10",
  "city": "Stuttgart",
  "country": "Germany",
  "region": "Baden-Wuerttemberg"
}

### 6. Disable branch (EPIC20-T6: native bound action, was POST /admin/disableBranch)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/Branches(fa2f6315-6576-404b-ae58-47c9e1769657)/AdminService.disable
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7. Create new user
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/createUser
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator.fischer@automarkt.de",
  "firstName": "Hans",
  "lastName": "Fischer",
  "phoneNumber": "+49 711 12345678",
  "roleCode": "Operator"
}

### 8. Assign role — add Manager role to new user (EPIC20-T6: native bound
### action, was POST /admin/assignRole)
### userId: replace with ID returned from step 7
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/Users(a842f2f6-042b-45c3-ac78-8c2cdbae87ed)/AdminService.assignRole
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleCode": "Manager"
}

### 9. Disable user (EPIC20-T6: native bound action, was POST /admin/disableUser)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/Users(a842f2f6-042b-45c3-ac78-8c2cdbae87ed)/AdminService.disable
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 10. List audit logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/AuditLogs
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 11. List event outbox
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/EventOutbox
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 12. Admin operation as Manager — should be rejected
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Users
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
